subject: FedEx Nigeria Head Office
body:
FedEx Nigeria Head Office
    70 International Airport Road
    Mafoluku, Lagos.
    Order: SH-5468-482485461
    Customers Service Hours--Monday to Saturday:
    Dear Customer,
    This is FedEx courier Delivery Company of Nigeria, the management of this
    company, wishes to inform you that, we received a parcel containing an ATM
    Master Card valued $2.5million USD with some vital documents attached on it,
    for safety delivery to your residential address in your country.
    This parcel was brought to us this morning by the ATM Card payment office
    Nigeria, with the below informationâ€™s, please reconfirm the below

    Full names............

    Country/State........

    Passport/Driving License
    Tel...........

    FedEx is one of the world's great success stories, the start-up that

    Waiting to read your

 )

subject: Re:   FedEx Nigeria Head Office
body:
Hello Mr. Onyx Perry,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm thrilled to hear about the ATM Master Card that has been delivered to your company for me. However, I must admit, this is quite a surprise as I wasn't expecting any such parcel.

Could you please provide more details about this? For instance, who sent this parcel and why was it sent to me? Also, could you clarify what the vital documents attached to it are?

I look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Marcia
